Package au.org.intersect.exsite9.domain

Interface Summary
IMetadataAssignable used for both Group and ResearchFile to return their metadata associations
 

Class Summary
ExcludedFilesGroup This group is a holder for files that have been excluded from the project.
FieldOfResearch Australian and New Zealand Standard Research Classification (ANZSRC), 2008.
Folder Represents a folder on the researcher's desktop that contains research data files
Group Represents a Group.
MetadataAssociation An association between a metadata category and it's values that have been assigned.
MetadataAttribute A metadata attribute.
MetadataAttributeValue the value entered for a metadata attribute for a ResearchFile or Group
MetadataCategory A metadata category.
MetadataCategoryViewConfiguration Holds view configuration details of a MetadataCategory
MetadataValue the values within a MetadataCategory
NewFilesGroup Used only to tag the New Files group of a project, so we can easily identify this group with instanceof checks.
Project Represents a Research Project
ResearchFile Represents a research data file in a folder that the researcher has associated with a project.
RootGroup The Root group - every project has one.
Schema Represents a Schema
SubmissionPackage A Submission Package is a collection of ResearchFiles that are to be bundled up for submission.
 

Enum Summary
MetadataCategoryType A Metadata Category type.
MetadataCategoryUse specifies whether a metadata category is required, recommended or optional
ResearchFileSearchDefinition Types of search available to the user
ResearchFileSortField The field to sort Groups on.
SortFieldDirection The direction to sort the a field with.
